author: chirino
msg: Removed the ability to consume from a pojo: endpoint since it is easier to consume from a direct: or queue: endpoint.

author: snicoll
msg: MPWAR-65: Added maven.war.expansion.excludes property to exclude files during a property expansion copy (Fixes corruption of binary files). Applied property expansion to web.xml handling for consistency. Introduced the maven.war.src.filtering property to control whether filtering is enabled or not when copying webapp resources.
